wm-license-cc-conditions-attribution-tex: Yessefk ad d-bedreḍ isem n umeskar aneṣli s wudem yettwammlen sɣuṛ ameskar n umahil neɣ bab n izerfan i k-imudden tasiregt (mačči s wudem yemmalen am akken yettmuddu-yak afus neɣ yeqbel aseqdec-it n umahil).
wm-license-cc-conditions-share_alike-tex: Ma tbeddleḍ, teskelteḍ, neɣ tebniḍ ɣef umahil-agi, yessefk ad tezzuzreḍ amahil i d-yeffɣen ɣas ddaw n turagt-nni neɣ turagt icuban ɣuṛ-s.
